      <h2>Explore Professional Training</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mx-auto" style="max-width: 720px;">Browse our software tracks and select a training path to view available softwares.</p>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-4" style="max-width: 500px; position: relative;">
        <input type="text" id="liveSearch" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="Search courses..." autocomplete="off">
        <div id="searchResults" class="list-group d-none position-absolute w-100 shadow" style="z-index: 1000; max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
