        <p class="section-desc">Practical project-based learning for architects, engineers, designers and surveyors. Each training track includes current tools used in the Rwandan and international building industry.</p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled feature-list">
          <li>
            <span class="badge rounded-pill me-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light)); color:#fff;">01</span>
            Hands-on workspace simulations.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="badge rounded-pill me-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light)); color:#fff;">02</span>
            Industry software for real tasks.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="badge rounded-pill me-2" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light)); color:#fff;">03</span>
            Internship-ready curriculum.
          </li>
        </ul>
