          </div>
          <p class="text-muted">Send your details and one of our advisors will contact you for registration and internship placement.</p>
          <form id="applyForm" action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjyzgjr" method="POST" class="row g-3">
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New course enquiry from City Building website">
            <div data-fs-success class="alert alert-success d-none" role="alert">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i> Thank you! We'll be in touch soon.
            </div>
